                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "呲牙裂扇箭"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素戰技</span></p><p>造成2點<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">岩元素傷害</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">，</span>生成<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">大將旗指物</span>。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">大將旗指物</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">出戰狀態</span></p><p>我方角色造成的<span style=\"color: #FFE699\">岩元素傷害</span>+1。</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">持續回合：２（</span>可疊加，最多疊加到3回合）</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/22/125391187/938b4e094906a85cee73a083091b261c_7256183205627657757.png",
                "key": "犬坂吠吠方圓陣",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "geo"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "犬坂吠吠方圓陣"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素爆發</span></p><p>造成2點<span style=\"color: #FFE699\">岩元素傷害</span>，生成<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">大將旗指物</span>，召喚<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">大將威儀</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/22/125391187/07aaa637ba933d0311335db4da950abf_5922842285669223090.png",
                "key": "獸牙逐突形勝戰法",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "geo"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "獸牙逐突形勝戰法"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">召喚物</span></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">結束階段：</span>造成1點<span style=\"color: #FFE699\">岩元素傷害</span>；如果隊伍中存在2名<span style=\"color: #FFE699\">岩元素角色</span>，則生成<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">結晶</span>。</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">可用次數：2</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/22/125391187/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_3520071108242748856.png",
                "key": "大將威儀",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/22/125391187/e473fedde5cae543bffc4ffb4faeef30_7930084792398798768.png",
                "title": "大將威儀"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>和已附著的元素發生元素反應：</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">岩元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">結晶（冰）</span>：本傷害+1，我方出戰角色獲得1點護盾（可疉加，最多2點）</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">岩元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">結晶（水）</span>：本傷害+1，我方出戰角色獲得1點護盾（可疉加，最多2點）</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">岩元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">結晶（火）</span>：本傷害+1，我方出戰角色獲得1點護盾（可疉加，最多2點）</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">岩元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">結晶（雷）</span>：本傷害+1，我方出戰角色獲得1點護盾（可疉加，最多2點）</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/22/125391187/fd37cbfdd3b1b2c16e6e83fb0aa96889_8983147086559192575.png",
                "key": "岩元素傷害",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "岩元素傷害"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">物理傷害</span></strong></p><p>物理傷害不會附著元素，也不會發生元素反應。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">持續回合</span></strong></p><p>每回合結束階段，<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">持續回合</span>-1；</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">持續回合</span>耗盡後，立刻棄置此牌。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次數</span></strong></p><p>此牌效果觸發後，會消耗一層可用次數；</p><p>可用次數耗盡後，立刻棄置此牌。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/22/125391187/07bae546ac7c69ef6402170b283840c5_197931565958686169.png",
